        "body": "<p>Thank you all !\nI started to use with this config and it's working fine from here <a href=\"https://docs.spring.io/spring/docs/current/spring-framework-reference/integration.html#scheduling-task-namespace-scheduled-tasks\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">https://docs.spring.io/spring/docs/current/spring-framework-reference/integration.html#scheduling-task-namespace-scheduled-tasks<\/a><\/p>\n\n<pre><code>&lt;task:scheduled-tasks scheduler=\"myScheduler\"&gt;\n    &lt;task:scheduled ref=\"beanA\" method=\"methodA\" fixed-delay=\"5000\" initial-delay=\"1000\"/&gt;\n    &lt;task:scheduled ref=\"beanB\" method=\"methodB\" fixed-rate=\"5000\"/&gt;\n    &lt;task:scheduled ref=\"beanC\" method=\"methodC\" cron=\"*/5 * * * * MON-FRI\"/&gt;\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n<p><\/p>\n",
